secondary_street_name: 28 Kirtling Street, 88 Kirtling Street and 2 Battersea Park Road
description: Partial amendment to the reserved matters and associated details relating to Phase 1, as approved on the 20th December 2012 (refs: 2012/4584 & 2012/4585) and the 8th May 2013 (refs: 2013/1192 & 2013/1193). The following amendments are proposed in this application: changes to the land use floor areas and mix, and internal access, at podium and basement levels; changes to the landscaping of the riverfront park and podium courtyard; removal of solar shading to non south-facing elevations; removal of colouring to the internal solar louvre screens and the removal of the fritting to the outer skins of the facades; amendments at rooftop level to a penthouse unit and to the ground level façade line as a result of structural coordination. (Details of the scale of the buildings and structures, external appearance of those buildings and structures, including facing materials, and landscaping; pursuant to condition 3 of the OPP).
